
/*
 * Restricts access to an HTTP endpoint to only specific roles using [auth.ticket.verify].
 *
 * 1. [auth.ticket.verify]
 *    * Ensures the caller has one of the authorized roles before continuing execution.
 *    * If the caller's role is not in the allowed list, an exception is thrown and the endpoint is blocked.
 *
 * In this case, only users with roles 'admin', 'marketing_manager', or 'c_exec' are allowed to invoke the endpoint.
 */
auth.ticket.verify:admin, marketing_manager, c_exec